*Information*
CTF Name: Bandit Level 7 - Level 8
Profile: OverTheWire
Difficulty: Easy
Description: The purpose of this level is to teach users how to use the grep command, which can be used to find patterns

*Content*
1) Connected to new level through using the username bandit7, with the password as the flag from the previous level. (A breakdown of the ssh 
command can be found in level0)
2) Used command 'grep "millionth" data.txt', with 'millionth' as the pattern after it was in the prompt
                  ^         ^          ^
              command    pattern  target file
